BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Mindful Petaluma
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/
UID:event_313845833@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T030205Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260407T193000
SUMMARY:Awakening Awareness: Embracing This Moment
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA session inspired by Eckhart Tolle's
  practices. Feel free to join as we get still and practise presence within
  this moment. We will discuss and observe the obstacles that\, seemingly\,
  block us from being present and bring awareness to our unconsciousness in
  a safe\, inclusive and affirming way.\n\nSessions are suitable for newcom
 ers\, those experienced in Tolle's teaching and anyone wishing to remain c
 ompletely anonymous.\n\nSee you there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions wi
 ll close if no members have joined after 10 minutes.\n\nEmrys has been pas
 sionate about mindfulness since 2010 and since 2021 he has been organising
  free\, weekly online meditation groups. For more information on his free 
 Work of Byron Katie online mediation group\, visit [this Meetup Group link
 ](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/).
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313845833/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260319T022030Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260319T022030Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Mindful Petaluma
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/
UID:event_313862625@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T030205Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260408T193000
SUMMARY:Beginners in The Work of Byron Katie: Newcomers Welcome
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\nA free Zoom meditation session design
 ed with newcomers in mind. Sessions will include at least one hour of faci
 litation (meditation) and there is room for questions and answers througho
 ut. If you're curious about The Work\, you're invited to join!\n\nSee you 
 there!\n\nPlease be aware that sessions will close if no members have join
 ed after 10 minutes.\n\n**To book a free introductory private session with
  Emrys\, [click here](https://calendly.com/mindfulnesswithemrys/onehourses
 sion)[.](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)**\n\nEmrys also orga
 nises a free Work of Byron Katie Meetup group. Visit: [https://www.meetup.
 com/thework-runsfree](https://www.meetup.com/thework-runsfree/)\n\n*Find o
 ut more about Emrys [here](https://mindfulnesswithemrys.business.site/)[.]
 (http://linktr.ee/theworkrunsfree)*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313862625/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260320T024926Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260320T024926Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Mindful Petaluma
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/
UID:event_313896881@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260407T030205Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T074500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260411T080500
SUMMARY:Inner Body Guided-Meditation 
DESCRIPTION:The Mindful Stream (CA)\n"Awareness of the inner body takes yo
 u beyond the mind." - Eckhart Tolle\n\nIn this mediation session we will b
 ring our attention here: to the inner body where we practise presence by f
 ocusing on our physical sensations.\n\nSessions are suitable for newcomers
 \, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wishing to remain com
 pletely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and cameras and microp
 hones will be disabled. (Depending on the situation\, a free discussion ma
 y be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nSessions are suita
 ble for newcomers\, those experienced in Tolle's teachings and anyone wish
 ing to remain completely anonymous. They will last around 20 minutes and c
 ameras and microphones will be disabled. (Depending on the situation\, a f
 ree discussion may be held at the end with mics and cameras allowed.)\n\nS
 ee you there!\n\nEmrys also organises a free Work of Byron Katie online me
 diation group. Visit [this Meetup Group link](https://www.meetup.com/thewo
 rk-runsfree/) for more information.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/mindfulnesspetaluma/events/313896881/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260322T160218Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260322T160218Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
